Package: alienarena2007
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, alienarena2007-data
Description: standalone 3D first person online deathmatch shooter
 ALIEN ARENA 2007 is a standalone 3D first person online deathmatch shooter crafted from the original source code of  Quake II and Quake III,  released by id Software under the GPL license.
 .
 This package installs the client for Alien Arena.
 .
 Homepage <http://red.planetarena.org>

Package: alienarena2007-server
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, alienarena2007, alienarena2007-data
Description: standalone 3D first person online deathmatch shooter
 ALIEN ARENA 2007 is a standalone 3D first person online deathmatch shooter crafted from the original source code of  Quake II and Quake III,  released by id Software under the GPL license.
 .
 This package installs the dedicated server for Alien Arena.
 .
 Homepage <http://red.planetarena.org>

Package: alienarena2007-data
Architecture: all
Recommends: alienarena2007
Description: standalone 3D first person online deathmatch shooter
 ALIEN ARENA 2007 is a standalone 3D first person online deathmatch shooter crafted from the original source code of  Quake II and Quake III,  released by id Software under the GPL license.
 .
 This package installs the data files needed to run Alien Arena.
 .
 Homepage <http://red.planetarena.org>
